  Performance Characteristics

  - Caesar: O(n) - linear in text length
  - Vigenère: O(n) - linear in text length
  - Playfair: O(n) - linear but with higher constant factor due to matrix lookups
  - Memory: O(1) - constant (except Playfair's 5×5 matrix = O(1))

  All algorithms are highly efficient for educational purposes, processing thousands of characters in milliseconds.

